{"tid":2318391,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中年工人涉藏雷射筆兼拒捕受審 警指被告被捕後情緒激動 向前仆致額頭流血","createTime":"2020-12-09T09:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T14:08:13.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d225cfdb9ecf7bf674289d56194d92757186815d","tid":2318391,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T09:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eDXMxQF0ptbqoUmPMua7DDm5rc0=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3X22TB3NCZGA5EPKK4JHDRVFVA.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeDXMxQF0ptbqoUmPMua7DDm5rc0%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3X22TB3NCZGA5EPKK4JHDRVFVA.JPG&h=113e618b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女警長郭嘉嘉<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JUqCemqlUSUCW2oKpVHiYE8m1qg=/802x1025/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WERMVG4JOVBA5CVDSFY3YKXVQA.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJUqCemqlUSUCW2oKpVHiYE8m1qg%3D%2F802x1025%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWERMVG4JOVBA5CVDSFY3YKXVQA.JPG&h=a7a09b6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員王立聰<br />\n<br />\n去年9月22日有市民在港鐵太子站外聚集，其間有人在旺角警署外噴漆。防暴警衝出驅散時，拘捕一名中年運輸工人，並指他被捕期間多番掙扎，帶返警署後又發現其背囊內格藏有雷射筆。涉案工人被控在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器及拒捕兩罪，案件今在西九龍裁判法院開審。<strong><span class=\"red\">負責拘捕的警員指，被告在搜身期間突然情緒激動，雙手帶上手銬後向前仆，導致右額流血。其後為他檢查時，再發現他背部多處有紅印。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n被告曾質疑警方濫權，今年5月底入稟區域法院，指控警方對他使用非法武力。<br />\n<br />\n警員王立聰聲稱，被告突然情緒激動，「用身體揈開我哋」，又稱「死黑警，收皮啦」。王稱被告想向前走，但因雙手遭手銬鎖上，故他失重心向前仆，左邊額頭仆在地上。王扶起他後，看見他左額有2厘米長的傷口，正在流血。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201209/GFGLLZNHFRAK7M4J6TH327L56Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201209%2FGFGLLZNHFRAK7M4J6TH327L56Q%2F&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUH6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=80b1ba37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201209%2FGFGLLZNHFRAK7M4J6TH327L56Q%2F&h=81b72a99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201209/GFGLLZNHFRAK7M4J6TH327L56Q/</a>"},{"pid":"f254e7697dd0ea9d1e79a8fdd6cbbe8a85d689b9","tid":2318391,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T09:54:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf902f03ffab8873cd043dbcaacbf0fbadffda3b","tid":2318391,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T09:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7c85c8e759ec32329fa3b35eebd458ef46f4d4","tid":2318391,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T09:55:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4da2765b1d7c04e10235bc372bac25418232bec2","tid":2318391,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T09:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79fe4d6a199899de7540d22417036ae82934aac","tid":2318391,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T09:58:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不如話佢撞埋你支棍到"},{"pid":"2e9ad75d29dba228ce3965210684320d2fe86956","tid":2318391,"uid":84409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T10:07:01.000Z","msg":"不如話被告被捕後自己打到自己骨折"},{"pid":"6fa7ef46547eb838c83ee007bf067b917e155fa3","tid":2318391,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T10:09:58.000Z","msg":"王稱，被告其後突然情緒激動，說「收皮啦，死黑警」，並用身體「揈開」警員。王形容，被鎖上手銬的被告想向前走，然後失重心跌落地下，及後王發現被告左額頭流血，有大約2cm傷口。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">被告在五月底曾入稟區院，指警方對他使用不合法武力，令他受傷及蒙受損失，要求警務處長賠償。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E9%81%8B%E8%BC%B8%E5%B7%A5%E5%90%A6%E8%A9%9E%E6%8A%97%E6%8B%92%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%AD%89%E7%BD%AA-%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6-%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%A1%E6%8E%99%E6%89%8E-%E8%A2%AB%E6%90%9C%E8%BA%AB%E6%99%82%E5%A4%B1%E9%87%8D%E5%BF%83%E8%B7%8C%E4%BD%8E%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%80/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E9%2581%258B%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25A9%259E%25E6%258A%2597%25E6%258B%2592%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25AD%2589%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%258E%2599%25E6%2589%258E-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2590%259C%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%25B7%258C%25E4%25BD%258E%25E6%25B5%2581%25E8%25A1%2580%2F&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaUH6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=76989b6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E9%2581%258B%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25A9%259E%25E6%258A%2597%25E6%258B%2592%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25AD%2589%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E6%258E%2599%25E6%2589%258E-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2590%259C%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%25B7%258C%25E4%25BD%258E%25E6%25B5%2581%25E8%25A1%2580%2F&h=c5714d58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E9%81%8B%E8%BC%B8%E5%B7%A5%E5%90%A6%E8%A9%9E%E6%8A%97%E6%8B%92%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%AD%89%E7%BD%AA-%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6-%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E5%A4%9A%E6%AC%A1%E6%8E%99%E6%89%8E-%E8%A2%AB%E6%90%9C%E8%BA%AB%E6%99%82%E5%A4%B1%E9%87%8D%E5%BF%83%E8%B7%8C%E4%BD%8E%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%80/<